description: You can ask for a quote from one of the following philosophers: Albert Camus, Franz Kafka, Simone de Beauvoir, Jean-Paul Sartre, Soren Kierkegaard, Friedrich Nietzsche, and Fyodor Dostoevsky (or let ExistentialQuotes pick one of them at random). Ask for help to hear this list of philosophers. This app pulls quotes from the Stands4 database. Their website is at quotes.net.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Existential Quotes to read a quote by Albert Camus.
Ask Existential Quotes to read a Random quote.
name: ExistentialQuotes
shortDescription: Existential Quotes can read a random quote from an existentialist philosopher of your choosing.
